title: (Fri) Maren Morris on Album Release Day + Comedian Jim Gaffigan on His Most Famous Jokes + Easy Trivia!
itunes:title: (Fri) Maren Morris on Album Release Day + Comedian Jim Gaffigan on His Most Famous Jokes + Easy Trivia!
description:
Maren Morris stops by to talk about the release of her new album “Humble Quest”, live shows and Grammys. Comedian Jim Gaffigan talks about his new tour, people repeating his jokes to him and if his kids think he’s funny. Plus our traditional round of Easy Trivia!
